  "lyrics": "[Music] ► ► With shadows and no longer cares We're being written at last Give you shares some secrets of Tails And if we agree, I'm complete all steel You'll have the whole truth, sprinkle with lies. O yimos, except some injustice. Do under the rat, Give your responses based on a sliver of faith that I love you. We're gonna be fine Nothin' left is a lapse We decide to entwine a pen You can play shabagage the next time But do not bring A lot of material things I have found that never said it's fine Or you must accept someone just to surrender to rap If your response is based on a sliver of faith that I'm We're gonna be fast ► Lift the last dreams left Down those rails to head We find ourselves left behind After the sad If we look into each other's hands And see some peace with no one that trained Then they must accept the injustice. Endure the wrath of your response can be traced to the lack of faith. We're gonna be back . ►",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 12,
      "text": "[Music]",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 23.5,
      "text": "►",
      "start": 11.5
    },
    {
      "end": 35,
      "text": "►",
      "start": 23
    },
    {
      "end": 46.5,
      "text": "With shadows and no longer cares We're being written at last Give you shares some secrets of Tails",
      "start": 34.5
    },
    {
      "end": 58,
      "text": "And if we agree, I'm complete all steel",
      "start": 46
    },
    {
      "end": 69.5,
      "text": "You'll have the whole truth, sprinkle with lies. O yimos, except some injustice.",
      "start": 57.5
    },
    {
      "end": 81,
      "text": "Do under the rat, Give your responses based on a sliver of faith that I love you.",
      "start": 69
    },
    {
      "end": 92.5,
      "text": "We're gonna be fine",
      "start": 80.5
    },
    {
      "end": 104,
      "text": "Nothin' left is a lapse We decide to entwine a pen",
      "start": 92
    },
    {
      "end": 115.5,
      "text": "You can play shabagage the next time But do not bring",
      "start": 103.5
    },
    {
      "end": 127,
      "text": "A lot of material things I have found that never said it's fine",
      "start": 115
    },
    {
      "end": 138.5,
      "text": "Or you must accept someone just to surrender to rap If your response is based on a sliver of faith that I'm",
      "start": 126.5
    },
    {
      "end": 150,
      "text": "We're gonna be fast",
      "start": 138
    },
    {
      "end": 161.5,
      "text": "►",
      "start": 149.5
    },
    {
      "end": 173,
      "text": "Lift the last dreams left Down those rails to head",
      "start": 161
    },
    {
      "end": 184.5,
      "text": "We find ourselves left behind After the sad",
      "start": 172.5
    },
    {
      "end": 196,
      "text": "If we look into each other's hands And see some peace with no one that trained",
      "start": 184
    },
    {
      "end": 207.5,
      "text": "Then they must accept the injustice. Endure the wrath of your response can be traced to the lack of faith.",
      "start": 195.5
    },
    {
      "end": 219,
      "text": "We're gonna be back",
      "start": 207
    },
    {
      "end": 230.5,
      "text": ".",
      "start": 218.5
    },
    {
